sentences: Steve Forde was born in the regional farming centre of Cowra, New South Wales in 1977.
Although retired now, Steve was a successful bull rider and bareback bronc rider.
At 18 years old, Ford joined his first band and tasted the life of a touring country musician.
He first left for the United States in 1998 he joined a country band in Texas and toured through Colorado, South Dakota and into Canada.
Steve headed back to Australia when he heard that his father needed help on the farm and he went to work on the farm, still doing rodeos during the weekends.
